reviewText: This is a great anime and this set is wonderful.

I love the series. Watched it more times than I can count and even went out of my way to search around for a DVD copy.

My only complaint is that this version of it has some messy and incorrect subtitles in many places. The DVD itself looks a lot like it was either really cheaply made or it was done by an unofficial company. However, since it was hard to find even this version Season 2, I overlook this little detail.

Outside the subtitles though, I have no real problems with this.
My daughter loves this series.  If you like volleyball and are into Japanese teen anime this is for you
